{"tid":48125,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"短篇「超能」「現實」「本土」喺香港想有超能力只係塞豆窿嘅諗法？","createTime":"2016-12-21T00:34:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T10:07:52.000Z","uid":9586,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9ba9bc54a635f9409435b3efc41ca67a73045824","tid":48125,"uid":9586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:34:35.000Z","msg":"呢個故希望幫大家搵返細蚊仔想成為英雄嘅童真，大個咗男人老狗為搵食，當年嘅幼稚揼到冇雷公咁遠，今日由我幫大家去執返返嚟，閃爆飛潛控回過夠本，希望大家畀啲火我<br />\n<br />\n時間表：<br />\n每星期岀一個短篇<br />\n每逢星期二岀文<br />\n<br />\n每日都會覆你哋嘅能力，太弱可能會加啲得意效果同玩法，而太強當然會減弱<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為太耐無寫過嘢，組織都好差希望大家有咩問題就講盡力屌，百屌成材，睇住我進步，上一篇畀個巴打問我啲中文係咪體育老師教，真係瘀到骨痹！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n世界觀：<br />\n每個主角都因應細個嘅諗法想做英雄嘅能力去衍生自己嘅能力，雖然有超能力但肉體上並無任何強化，需要自己去做練習<br />\n<br />\n有乜想要嘅能力暫時夠啦，太多寫唔到就無謂，但鐘意嘅都可以留言，排到尖沙咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n岀發啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eb73aa5d9a7ea09f9d479725e7d453ef5db4dd2","tid":48125,"uid":36072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:49:17.000Z","msg":"冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b00d87055277a4cbeb49118a518f42ee82f7c44c","tid":48125,"uid":50235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:12:22.000Z","msg":"文呢？"},{"pid":"6399de54a010f271cf165a590ebd923ef3a3c850","tid":48125,"uid":25902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T12:04:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec3132c98448fde78c7aab872730fb13624232e4","tid":48125,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0